textbook. In the table below, such problems are simply referred to using
the section number and problem number from the textbook. When additional
(outside the textbook) problems are assigned, they are numbered AP1,
AP2, etc. To read the statements of these problems, see the <a
href="additional.pdf">additional problems page</a>, or just click on
the problem number in the table below. </p>

