<a name=solutions></a>
<h3>Solutions to Homework and Exam Problems</h3>

<p> Here is a collection of links to PDF files containing solutions to
problems from the textbook. Some of the solutions are detailed and
explain all of the reasoning involved. But many of them are outlines
only and in a homework or an exam you should provide a little more
detailed reasoning. These solutions were prepared by Professors Ken
Bogart, Scot Drysdale and Cliff Stein. <b>Please do not distribute
them</b>. </p>

<p> There may be typos in the solutions. If you find any, please notify
me so I can notify the authors. </p>

